# 5. Lists in HTML

## Ordered List

```html
<ol>
    <li>Python</li>
    <li>Java</li>
    <li>JavaScript</li>
</ol>
```

## Unordered List

```html
<ul>
    <li>HTML</li>
    <li>CSS</li>
    <li>Bootstrap</li>
</ul>
```

