# 9. Forms in HTML

## Example

```html
<form>

    <label>Name:</label>
    <input type="text">

    <br><br>

    <label>Password:</label>
    <input type="password">

    <br><br>

    <input type="submit">

</form>
```

---

# 10. Semantic Tags in HTML5

